</entry></row>
<row><entry align="right"><parameter>screen_num</parameter>&nbsp;:</entry>
<entry> Screen number.
</entry></row>
<row><entry align="right"><parameter>prefDepth</parameter>&nbsp;:</entry>
<entry> Preferred depth for XlibRGB.
</entry></row>
</tbody></tgroup></informaltable></refsect2>

